==设施==
===旧馆舍===

重庆图书馆旧馆舍位于重庆市[[渝中区|渝中区]]长江一路十一号（两路口馆区）和枇杷山正街九十三号（枇杷山馆区）<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 中国图书馆网 | title = 重庆图书馆简介 | url = http://www.chnlib.com/Ggtsg/1785.html | date = 2005-11-26 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，前者交通方便但藏书仅20万册，后者资料齐全但是交通不畅，且馆舍自1947年使用至2007年，面临建筑设施陈旧老化的问题<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 易书网 | title = 图书馆的压力：重庆图书馆现状 | url = http://www.ydbook.com/books/bkview.asp?bkid=46559&cid=88574 | author = 李顺军 | date = 2003-10-07 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-date = 2019-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190630214745/http://www.ydbook.com/books/bkview.asp?bkid=46559&cid=88574 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，自2007年3月1日起，旧馆舍开始闭馆搬迁，到2007年6月搬迁完毕<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 新华网 | title = 老馆走过60年历程  重庆图书馆将迁新址 | url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/book/2007-02/27/content_5778355.htm | date = 2007-02-27 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090917173345/http://news.xinhuanet.com/book/2007-02/27/content_5778355.htm | archivedate = 2009-09-17 }}</ref>。2008年4月8日，两路口馆舍在完成维修工程之后，改为[[重庆市少年儿童图书馆|重庆市少年儿童图书馆]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 重庆机关党建网 | title = 重庆市少年儿童图书馆顺利完成搬迁工作 | url = http://www.cqjgdj.gov.cn/show.aspx?id=25748&cid=249 | date = 2008-04-28 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。枇杷山馆区现在是重庆图书馆历史文献中心。

自2000年至2006年，重庆图书馆旧馆舍共接待读者1532694人次，外借图书371300人次，外借图书1164582册次<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 搜狐 | title = 风雨60年 重庆图书馆今闭馆 | url = http://news.sohu.com/20070301/n248422928.shtml | date = 2007-03-01 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-date = 2019-06-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190601032202/http://news.sohu.com/20070301/n248422928.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>

===新馆舍===
[[Image:CQLIB-SouthGate.jpg|thumb]]
[[Image:CQLIB-Wall.jpg|thumb]]

重庆图书馆新馆舍位于[[沙坪坝区|沙坪坝区]]凤天大道106号，2007年6月14日竣工并开放了阅览室<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 新华网 | title = 时尚气派　重庆图书馆新馆今开门迎客 | url = http://www.cq.xinhuanet.com/photonews/2007-06/14/content_10292587.htm | author = 蒙春音 | date = 2007-06-14 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，在完成了文献的规整和计算机系统的测试之后，2008年年初开放了所有的服务窗口<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 华龙网 | title = 重庆图书馆全年天天对外开放 | url = http://cqtoday.cqnews.net/system/2008/09/11/001300987.shtml | author = 秦杰 | date = 2008-09-11 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

新馆舍投资3亿元人民币，占地面积50381平方米，藏书量可以达到500万册，每天能为5000到8000人次提供服务，并提供3000个阅读座位，为600多台电脑提供互联网接入<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = CCTV.com | title = 重庆图书馆新馆竣工开馆 投资额三亿元(图) | url = http://discovery.cctv.com/20070615/108215.shtml | author = 春天 | date = 2007-06-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archive-date = 2019-06-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190608055247/http://discovery.cctv.com/20070615/108215.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。馆舍由美国[[Perkins_Eeastman|Perkins Eeastman]]公司设计<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Perkins Eeastman | title = Chongqing Library | url = http://www.perkinseastman.com/projectDetails.aspx?p=2400291&c=2400019 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101006120600/http://perkinseastman.com/projectDetails.aspx?p=2400291&c=2400019 | archivedate = 2010-10-06 }}</ref>，获得了美国“2009年图书馆设计奖”<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-hans|author=王明明|coauthors=许姜媛、徐健镜|title=重庆图书馆获美国2009设计大奖——气度非凡的美丽 声名显赫的身世|url=http://sdxbepaper.cqnews.net/sdxb/html/2009-08/28/content_966315.htm|work=时代信报|publisher=|date=2009-08-28|accessdate=2010-04-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929004913/http://sdxbepaper.cqnews.net/sdxb/html/2009-08/28/content_966315.htm|archivedate=2012-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher =  | title = AIA and ALA Name Library Award Winners | url = http://www.interiordesign.net/article/CA6643651.html | author = Nicholas Tamarin | date = 2009-03-16 | accessdate = 2010-04-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100330205544/http://www.interiordesign.net/article/CA6643651.html | archivedate = 2010-03-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

